@startuml nav_alert_context_to_dcm_request_response_observation_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Nav Alert Context To DCM Request Response Observation Signal Flow\n(nav/session + alert context -> DCM diagnostic request/response observation seams)

participant "Navigation /\ncluster-notif context" as NavCtx #F4F7FB
participant "Boundary state /\nfail-safe context" as Boundary #E8F0FE
participant "DCM\ndiagnostic owner" as DCM #E8F7E8
participant "Diag sysvar seams" as DiagBus #FFF4CC
participant "Observers /\nservice readers" as Obs #FCE8FF

== DCM Inputs ==

NavCtx -> DCM : frmNavModuleStateMsg\nNavSessionState / NavRouteClass
NavCtx -> DCM : frmClusterNotifMsg\nClusterNotifArg
Boundary -> DCM : CoreState::domainBoundaryStatus\nCoreState::warningPathStatus\nCore::failSafeMode
activate DCM
DCM -> DCM : routeActive = recent nav session/route class
DCM -> DCM : alertLevel = recent cluster-notif arg
DCM -> DCM : serviceContext =\nethHasBoundaryServiceContext(routeActive, alertLevel)
DCM -> DCM : diagStage = ethDiagBoundaryStage(...)\nfrom route/alert/boundary/fail-safe context
DCM -> DCM : securitySession / authState /\nsecurityFault / securityPolicy
DCM -> DCM : serviceState / responseKind /\nreasonCode / responseCode
note right of DCM
Representative gating inputs
- NavSessionState
- NavRouteClass
- ClusterNotifArg
- domainBoundaryStatus
- warningPathStatus
- failSafeMode
end note

== Diag Observation Publish ==

DCM -> DiagBus : Diag::ServiceState / ResponseKind / ReasonCode
DCM -> DiagBus : Diag::LastRequest* / RequestCounter
DCM -> DiagBus : Diag::LastResponse* / ResponseCounter
note right of DCM
Representative outputs
- ServiceState
- ResponseKind
- LastRequestSid
- LastResponseCode
- RequestCounter / ResponseCounter
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

DiagBus -> Obs : diagnostic observation /\nservice and reviewer-facing readers
deactivate DCM

note over NavCtx, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Navigation and alert context reach DCM
2. DCM combines them with boundary and fail-safe state
3. DCM derives diagnostic stage and request/response posture
4. DCM publishes request/response observation seams on Diag
end note

@enduml
